getting pregnant or beat up.

28
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,432
That's sayin' somethin'.

29
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:09,799
Well. Speak of the devil.

30
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:15,273
Ain't he a mess.

31
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:18,597
Works his mama's books upstairs
and God-knows-what on the side.

32
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,796
- Must be a drug dealer.
- Hardly.

33
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,355
Real estate, stocks,
that kinda stuff.

34
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:26,399
He's one can make money
when all the news is bad.

35
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:29,996
- It's a good trick.
- Yeah, for him, maybe.

36
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:13,354
I was here once when
I was 10 years old.

37
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:16,954
Only vacation I can remember.

38
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:20,192
Yeah. Summer's fine.

39
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:23,832
On the other hand, this
time of year's kinda bleak.

40
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:27,116
Seems fine to me.

41
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:30,270
If you like ghosts, maybe.

42
