110
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:38,993
<i>Debrah Ann?</i>

111
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:41,518
<i>Guess what I got?</i>

112
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,831
<font color="#ffff00">Nothing fancy here.</font>

113
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:45,514
<font color="#ffff00">Just try to put down
my thinking over time.</font>

114
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:51,630
<font color="#ffff00">Maybe figure out the why's of
running off, of coming here.</font>

