117
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:07,158
<font color="#ffff00">It was "Do this, do that."</font>

118
00:16:08,800 --> 00:16:13,078
<font color="#ffff00">Now it's up to me,
to what I want to be.</font>

119
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:19,473
<font color="#ffff00">I got some idea about inside,</font>

120
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,589
<font color="#ffff00">feelings and stuff.</font>

121
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:26,031
<font color="#ffff00">But about the outside,</font>

122
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:29,756
<font color="#ffff00">the acts and looks of things,</font>

123
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:33,192
<font color="#ffff00">of me,</font>

124
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:37,876
<font color="#ffff00">I am not so clear.</font>

125
00:16:44,760 --> 00:16:47,638
<font color="#ffff00">Wonder if I'll ever feel
just what I am.</font>

126
00:17:21,600 --> 00:17:22,749
No...

127
00:17:23,120 --> 00:17:25,270
No, you're right, you're right,
it may never be the same.

128
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:28,959
<i>Those little bastards love nothing more
than to make trouble for business.</i>

129
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:34,794
<i>Uh-huh. Leeches is what
they are, worthless.</i>

130
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:40,718
<i>No! No, no.
It shouldn't affect the deal.</i>

131
00:17:41,720 --> 00:17:44,280
Thirty dollars and
seventy-three cents, please.

132
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:46,238
<i>No. Not at this time, at least.</i>

133
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:48,996
Hey, I'll keep you informed, okay?

134
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:53,272
Here you go. Your receipt.
<i>Listen, JB, if I'm gonna meet
Justine in a half-hour, I gotta go.</i>

135
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:55,359
<i>JB...</i>

136
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:58,029
<i>Five bucks says I take you by 3.</i>

137
00:17:58,823 --> 00:18:00,674
<i>Oh. Okay, buddy. You're on.</i>

138
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:17,115
- See you later.
- Are you leaving?

139
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:20,517
- Huh. It's dead.
