141
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,514
Trust me.

142
00:18:31,760 --> 00:18:34,320
- So how about tonight?
- Excuse me?

143
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:35,549
Dinner, dancing?

144
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:40,954
