147
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:51,034
And for another, your mama says that
the help stays clear of the boss' son.

148
00:18:51,760 --> 00:18:53,591
My mama tries to protect me
from opportunists, but uh...

149
00:18:53,760 --> 00:18:57,070
I can take care of myself.

150
00:18:58,560 --> 00:18:59,788
Can you?

151
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:04,355
