<font color="#ffff00">So far, fun has been nothing but work.</font>

157
00:24:32,040 --> 00:24:35,669
<font color="#ffff00">Ricky was right:
get it over with.</font>

158
00:25:14,800 --> 00:25:17,519
Morning. Sorry I'm late.

159
00:25:38,320 --> 00:25:39,548
Here.

160
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:43,995
It's for those lonely nights
