161
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:47,397
I really enjoyed our evening.

162
00:25:50,760 --> 00:25:52,398
We'll do it again sometime.

163
00:25:53,560 --> 00:25:55,471
I'll get the cash drawer.

164
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:57,836
Another day, another dollar.
I hope.

165
00:25:58,840 --> 00:26:01,479
Do something with that towel display
when you get a chance.

166
00:26:02,320 --> 00:26:04,356
