169
00:26:33,160 --> 00:26:36,436
Alright, I guess.
Mrs. Chambers has been on vacation.

170
00:26:36,600 --> 00:26:39,592
So you've been alone with the masher?
He come onto you yet?

171
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:42,117
I keep him at arm's length.

172
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:44,438
Besides, half the time
he's not even there.

173
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:48,076
That's good, see, cause he's the kind
