<font color="#ffff00">"to die."</font>

477
01:02:15,000 --> 01:02:18,276
- Wish I had a set of these.
- Let's see the price.

478
01:02:23,640 --> 01:02:26,712
Woody, I'll take a dozen
of each of the trays.

479
01:02:56,200 --> 01:02:57,872
You keep all of this in your head?

480
01:02:58,320 --> 01:03:01,312
Well, most of it doesn't change,
just the numbers.

481
01:03:01,480 --> 01:03:03,755
and what you think
you can sell this year.

482
01:03:26,480 --> 01:03:29,677
Ms. Chambers,
I need to know something.

483
01:03:31,880 --> 01:03:33,598
Am I doing a good job?

484
01:03:34,880 --> 01:03:36,757
Well, you still have a lot to learn.

485
01:03:37,760 --> 01:03:40,399
