I guess you've been to a lot of trade shows.

508
01:06:37,080 --> 01:06:38,832
Not since I could say "no".

509
01:06:40,640 --> 01:06:43,677
Your mom spent $6,000
in four hours on the floor.

510
01:06:43,840 --> 01:06:48,152
Then we went to a big meeting about
tourism, and ate in a fancy restaurant,

511
01:06:48,320 --> 01:06:52,552
and got some sleep before hitting
the floor again this morning, then
drove straight back through

512
01:06:52,960 --> 01:06:55,997
so you can see how I'm real worn out.

513
01:07:06,640 --> 01:07:07,868
Ruby!

514
01:07:08,600 --> 01:07:11,910
I ain't seen anybody since you.
I got feelings, don't you understand?

515
01:07:15,120 --> 01:07:17,190
I just need you to set them free.

516
01:07:18,520 --> 01:07:20,954
And everything'll be all right.

517
01:07:29,200 --> 01:07:31,714
